{"tid":2281532,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劉兆佳：基本法列明褫奪議員資格條文不足應付目前局面","createTime":"2020-11-11T08:46:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-11T10:57:36.000Z","uid":66324,"like":29,"dislike":60,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"a645cf2401658334e5277a97423f3defffa1bdac","tid":2281532,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T08:46:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1559453-20201111.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1559453-20201111.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=yH4nd0T6GS6ufvAy6eHVEdg1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=3a4a7346\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1559453-20201111.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=0fd95bc1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1559453-20201111.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n&quot;劉兆佳認為香港從來不缺反對聲音及制衡力量，這些來自輿論、民意、社會各種反對勢力、民間團體，甚至<span class=\"red\">西方媒體</span>。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;他說，香港目前已沒有溫和民主派，尤其立法會內都是激進反對派，中央希望有較健康的<span class=\"red\">忠誠反對派</span>出現，願意在憲制及《基本法》框架內運作。至於目前的民主派人士是否已難以再入閘進入議會，劉兆佳認為目前言之尚早，要視乎民主派是否願意調整立場，但承認難以改變；<span class=\"red\">中央是定出規矩，讓民主派培養新血，或讓新人冒起，以忠誠反對派的身分去參政。</span>&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a7658672218abcd495665a79b505c457eeb2847","tid":2281532,"uid":58630,"like":78,"dislike":1,"score":77,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T08:49:01.000Z","msg":"以前建制全部都要100%支持 而家終於有得扮反對 唔洗成日做死一個角色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"980a0acae02d9bf20a471b513cdf6b6bf6924bd9","tid":2281532,"uid":271894,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T08:49:55.000Z","msg":"姐係民建聯B隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmo